      "text": "據《世說新語．尤悔》篇說，任城王曹彰之死是由於曹丕忌\n恨他的驍勇，給他吃了毒棗。這段記載僅供參考。薨：古代稱諸侯或有\n爵位的大官死去為「薨」",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-4",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 0,
        "start": 42,
        "end": 44
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "藩王回自己的封地",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-5",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 0,
        "start": 46,
        "end": 48
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "官吏，這裏指曹丕設立的監察諸王、傳達詔令的監國使者灌均",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-6",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 0,
        "start": 54,
        "end": 60
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "指藩王在路上不能同行同宿",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-7",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 0,
        "start": 68,
        "end": 70
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "永別。因藩國之間不能互相往來，所以分手後很難再見",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-8",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 0,
        "start": 76,
        "end": 78
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "剖白自己的內心",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-9",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 0,
        "end": 1
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "yue",
      "text": "咽；jit3",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-10",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 0,
        "end": 1
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "cmn",
      "text": "yè",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-11",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 0,
        "end": 1
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "朝見。承明廬：長安漢代宮殿名，借指皇帝接見的宮殿。\n謁：；亦讀作[揭]，[kit3]",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-12",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 6,
        "end": 7
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "往。舊疆：自己的封地",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-13",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 15,
        "end": 17
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "皇城，指洛陽",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-14",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 21,
        "end": 23
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "山名。在洛陽東北二十里",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-15",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 2,
        "start": 0,
        "end": 1
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "水名，源出河南熊耳山，至偃師縣入洛水。洛：洛水。源出陜西冢\n嶺山，至河南鞏縣入黃河",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-16",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 2,
        "start": 7,
        "end": 8
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "渡河。梁：橋",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-17",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 2,
        "start": 14,
        "end": 17
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "指渡過伊水和洛水",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-18",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 2,
        "start": 20,
        "end": 22
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "指返回封地鄄城的路",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-19",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 2,
        "start": 24,
        "end": 26
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "回頭眺望。城闕：指洛陽",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-20",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 2,
        "start": 30,
        "end": 32
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "伸長脖子，極目遠望",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-21",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 3,
        "start": 0,
        "end": 2
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "舊名「通谷」，在洛陽東南五十里。一說為山谷名，一說為關\n名。寥廓：空闊",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-22",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 3,
        "start": 12,
        "end": 14
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "連續不斷的大雨。泥我途：使我走的道路泥濘不堪。史載黃初四\n年六月大雨，伊、洛泛濫",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-23",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 3,
        "start": 18,
        "end": 20
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "yue",
      "text": "老；lou5",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-24",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 3,
        "start": 18,
        "end": 20
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "cmn",
      "text": "lɑ̌o",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-25",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 3,
        "start": 18,
        "end": 20
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "流水淤積。潦：；。浩縱橫：浩漫橫溢",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-26",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 3,
        "start": 24,
        "end": 26
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "道路交錯之處。逵：四通八達的大路。軌：車跡",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-27",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 3,
        "start": 30,
        "end": 32
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "車子改道",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-28",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 3,
        "start": 36,
        "end": 38
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "yue",
      "text": "措；cou3",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-29",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 3,
        "start": 36,
        "end": 38
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "長長的斜坡。造：到達，",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-30",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 3,
        "start": 44,
        "end": 47
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "馬病變色。《 詩經．周南．卷耳》：「陟彼高岡，我馬玄\n黃。」",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-31",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 4,
        "start": 8,
        "end": 11
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "心情鬱結",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-32",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 4,
        "start": 18,
        "end": 20
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "指親兄弟。在離居：即將分居兩地",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-33",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 4,
        "start": 24,
        "end": 26
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "本來打算。相與偕：兩人結伴而行",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-34",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 4,
        "start": 30,
        "end": 32
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "yue",
      "text": "庚；gang1",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-35",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 4,
        "start": 30,
        "end": 32
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "cmn",
      "text": "gēng",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-36",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 4,
        "start": 30,
        "end": 32
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "中途變更。更：；。不克：不能。俱：在\n一起",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-37",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 4,
        "start": 36,
        "end": 38
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "yue",
      "text": "雌；ci1",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-38",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 4,
        "start": 36,
        "end": 38
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "cmn",
      "text": "chī",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-39",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 4,
        "start": 36,
        "end": 38
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "鳥類的一種，頭大，嘴短而彎曲。吃鼠、兔、昆蟲等，古人認為\n是不祥之鳥。衡：車轅上的橫木。軛：衡兩旁下面用以扼住馬頸的曲\n木。這句比喻小人在皇帝身邊搬弄口舌。鴟：",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-40",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 4,
        "start": 42,
        "end": 47
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "用豺狼當道比喻壞人掌權",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-41",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 4,
        "start": 48,
        "end": 53
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "蒼蠅污白為黑，污黑為白，比喻邪惡小人顛倒黑白",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-42",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 4,
        "start": 54,
        "end": 56
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "讒言巧語。令親疏：令親骨肉疏遠",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-43",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 4,
        "start": 60,
        "end": 62
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "想回京城。絕無蹊：絕無歸路",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-44",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 5,
        "start": 18,
        "end": 20
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "蟬的一種，深秋時才停止鳴叫",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-45",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 5,
        "start": 34,
        "end": 35
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "藏，指太陽西下",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-46",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 5,
        "start": 44,
        "end": 45
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "振翅疾飛",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-47",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 5,
        "start": 51,
        "end": 53
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "yue",
      "text": "摵；saak3",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-48",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 5,
        "start": 51,
        "end": 53
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "尋找同伴。索：",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-49",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 5,
        "start": 56,
        "end": 58
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "沒有閑暇",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-50",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 5,
        "start": 69,
        "end": 71
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "嘆息",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-51",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 6,
        "start": 6,
        "end": 11
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "天命與我的心願相違背",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-52",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 6,
        "start": 18,
        "end": 23
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "指任城王一死，形體再不能歸來",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-53",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 6,
        "start": 24,
        "end": 29
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "指任城王的孤魂將飛回他生前的封地",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-54",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 6,
        "start": 36,
        "end": 41
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "活着的人日子很快也會過去",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-55",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 6,
        "start": 42,
        "end": 47
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "指生者隨着身體衰朽而自然死去",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-56",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 6,
        "start": 58,
        "end": 59
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "曬乾",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-57",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 6,
        "start": 60,
        "end": 65
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "桑、榆為二星名，都在西方。日暮時分，太陽運行位置在\n桑榆二星之間，古人據此觀察時辰。日在桑榆，比喻人到老年",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-58",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 6,
        "start": 66,
        "end": 67
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "指日光。響：指聲音。這句比喻時光快得連光和聲都追不上",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-59",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 6,
        "start": 72,
        "end": 77
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "自知人生沒有金石那麼永久",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-60",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 6,
        "start": 78,
        "end": 80
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "yue",
      "text": "胐責；deot1zaak3",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-61",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 6,
        "start": 78,
        "end": 80
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "cmn",
      "text": "duōjiè",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-62",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 6,
        "start": 78,
        "end": 80
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "悲嘆聲。咄唶：；亦讀作[綴責]，\n[zyut3zaak3]；；亦讀作[duōjiē]",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-63",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 7,
        "start": 21,
        "end": 23
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "yue",
      "text": "備；bei6",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-64",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 7,
        "start": 21,
        "end": 23
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "貼近的鄰居。比：",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-65",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 7,
        "start": 24,
        "end": 29
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "兄弟恩情如果沒有減弱",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-66",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 7,
        "start": 30,
        "end": 35
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "離得越遠，情分越是與日俱增。分：情分",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-67",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 7,
        "start": 38,
        "end": 41
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "yue",
      "text": "襟；kam1",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "9-68",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 7,
